a program step-by-step. A free online tool called the 

<link id="a1052" url="http://pythontutor.com/visualize.html#mode=edit">

Online Python Tutor

</link>

 
makes this possible. 

<emphasis id="em1016" effect="italics">
(You have seen some output from this tool in earlier 
modules. I will provide a more detailed explanation of how to use the tool in 
the module titled 

</emphasis>



<link id="a1053" url="http://cnx.org/contents/71aca310-6390-40c4-9001-561cde902a0c">




<emphasis id="em1017" effect="italics">
Itse1359-1065-Visualizing Python

